neat

Class NEAT

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.AbstractComponent
      • core.AbstractRepresentation
        • neat.NEAT
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<AbstractRepresentation>

    public class NEAT
extends AbstractRepresentation
    NeuroEvolution of Augmenting Topologies
    A neural network whose structure is also evolved.
    See http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neuroevolution_of_augmenting_topologies

    Originally developed by Ken Stanley in 2002 while at The University of Texas at Austin
